<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/3417391-mary">Mary</a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">This book is by the man himself, unbroken is not. This book is more broad, about his entire life. Shorter less emphasis on the prison camps. It also o<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">This book is by the man himself, unbroken is not. This book is more broad, about his entire life. Shorter less emphasis on the prison camps. It also offers his thoughts and opinions on things, especially on how he survived and what he thought of folks he met along the way. I loved them both just different perspective I guess. The story of the man is the same. <a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
</div>
