        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer4265602756" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer10044840202906263810">An excellent book. Deserves more than five stars! It is a retelling of Unbroken, this time from the viewpoint of the main character in Unbroken. This guy was an Olympic runner; served in WWII; was afloat on the ocean for weeks and assumed dead by the Army; and suffered in a Japanese prisoner of war camp.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


