<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/34017088-never-call-me-a-hero"><img alt="Never Call Me a Hero: A Legendary American Dive-Bomber Pilot Remembers the Battle of Midway" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1492708084l/34017088._SX98_.jpg" />
